Ing '''kabayu''' (''Equus ferus caballus'')<ref name=MSW3>{{MSW3 Perissodactyla | id = 14100016 | pages = 630–631}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=International Commission on Zoological Nomenclature|year=2003|title=Usage of 17 specific names based on wild species which are pre-dated by or contemporary with those based on domestic animals (Lepidoptera, Osteichthyes, Mammalia): conserved. Opinion 2027 (Case 3010)|journal=Bull.Zool.Nomencl.|volume=60|issue=1|pages=81–84|url=http://www.nhm.ac.uk/hosted_sites/iczn/BZNMar2003opinions.htm|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20070821235959/http://www.nhm.ac.uk/hosted_sites/iczn/BZNMar2003opinions.htm|archivedate=2007-08-21}}</ref> metung ya kareng adwang [[Extant taxon|mabyeng]] [[subspecies]] ning [[wild horse|''Equus ferus'']]. Metung yang [[ungulate a gansal taliring bitis]] ampong [[mammal]] a kayabe king familia [[Equidae]]. Meyalkus ya ing kabayu kareng milabasan a 45 anggang 55&nbsp;milyung banwa manibat king [[Hyracotherium|malating lelangan a dakal taliring bitis]] at megi yang maragul a animal a tunggal taliring bitis ngeni. Migumpisan rong patunuran ampong sesen deng tau deng kabayu kanitang manga 4000 BC, at paniwalan dang mikalat na ing pangatunud da reng kabayu anyang manga 3000 BC. Matunud la reng kabayu king subspecies a ''caballus'', oneng mebulus no reng aliwang matunud a kabayu at mebulus lang pasibayu. E la taganang malyap o ''wild'' deng populasyun a mebulus a reni, uling ing terminu o katayang ita gagamitan de kareng kabayung e bitasang metunud, antimo ing mamiligru nang mawalang  [[Przewalski's horse]], a makakawaning subspecies, a yang bukud namung ''wild'' o malyap a kabayu.
